This vibrant coastal watercolor moving announcements let friends and family know about your new home sweet home! The design features my original hand painted watercolor sea turtle and ocean waves shoreline in tropical shades of blue, turquoise and green. Your custom announcement (shown with "we’ve moved" and can be personalized to read "to the beach" or whatever you like), your name(s) and change of address details are set in a hand lettered script typography and traditional sans font in a rich navy blue. Add a personalized message to friends and family on the reverse side of this postcard size card with space for your stamp and recipient addressing.
